ğŸ¤– AI Semantic Analysis (Groq)

The system uses Llama 3.1 8B Instant via Groq for deep semantic evaluation.
It detects:

Patterned sentence structure

High coherence & uniformity typical of AI

Grammar consistency

Contextual fingerprints of LLM-generated text

It responds with structured JSON:

{"label": "AI", "confidence": 92, "reason": "Highly consistent patterns"}

ğŸ§  Linguistic Complexity Analysis

Wavein also performs local analysis on the text, including:

